column5: For some reason i just feel that i catch more fish when i don't bring my camera.  But it's just a superstitions now i only don't do it on tournament days lol.
In order for me to have a good day i have to be prepared with all of my gear the night before, i dont know why I just always seem to do better when im ready the night before.
If i catch a fish on the first cast i wont catch anything for the rest of the day.
I don't have any superstitions, but if I forget my camera I always end up catching something really nice
It's a bad sign when you get to your favorite lake and you see this.
